node.text: Catch up with the Nick’s! We talk about our upcoming plans together and what y’all should be expecting in the upcoming weeks. Cant wait for y’all to hear about our near future opportunities 😎🙌 @nickmasc

Remember- 
Each scoop provides
10 grams of refined and extremely absorbable protein. They also add Hyaluronic acid to provide so much more health benefits than a normal collagen product. It’s designed to supercharge any meal or drink! 🥞🥤☕️ 

Summary: Vital Proteins Collegen provides powerful recovering abilities while rejuvenating your hair, skin, nails, bones, and joints.
